Products.SmallFormatDescription: Masterfoods Stir Fry Sauce Honey, Garlic & Soy
Products.FullDescription: Masterfoods Stir Fry Sauce Honey, Garlic & Soy
Products.RichDescription:
Bring together honey, garlic and soy for a delicious stir fry.


Transform your stir-fry's with MasterFoods™ Honey, Garlic & Soy Stir Fry Recipe Base Sauce. Infuse flavour into your favourite fresh vegetables with plenty of honey, garlic and soy. Simply add lean chicken breast, red capsicum, broccoli and carrots for a delicious meal you can enjoy as part of your daily diet.

Preparation: 10 mins | Cook: 15 mins | Serves: 4

What You'll Need:

  • Canola Oil Spray
  • 500 g lean Chicken Breast, sliced
  • 1 MasterFoods™ Honey, Garlic & Soy Stir Fry Recipe Base
  • 2 Red Capsicum (400 g), deseeded & sliced
  • 1 Head of Broccoli, (190 g) cut into small florets
  • 3 Carrots (300 g), thinly sliced
  • 1 cup dry Brown Rice

How To Cook:
1. Heat pan on medium heat, spray with oil and cook chicken until browned.
2. Add Recipe Base and heat through.
3.Stir in vegetables and cook for 3-4 minutes or until vegetables are soft.
4. Meanwhile cook rice to serve with your MasterFoods™ Honey, Garlic & Soy Stir Fry.

For Something Different:
For a vegetarian option, swap the chicken with 450 g of firm tofu.


Blended with MasterFoods™ Herbs & Spices


Make Dinnertime Matter with MasterFoods™.

Products.SmallFormatDescription: Masterfoods Mild Chicken Curry Slow Cook Recipe Base
Products.FullDescription: Masterfoods Mild Chicken Curry Slow Cook Recipe Base
Products.RichDescription:
Discover a mouth-watering curry the whole family will love.


Discover the secret to a low fuss, mouth-watering dinner with MasterFoods™ Mild Chicken Curry Slow Cook Recipe Base. Made with a traditional blend of aromatic herbs and spices including cumin, coriander and turmeric. Just add lean chicken breast, onion, carrots, potatoes and light cream for a delicious meal you can enjoy as part of your daily diet.

Preparation: 15 mins | Cook: 8 hours | Serves: 4

What You'll Need:

  • Canola Oil Spray
  • 500 g lean Chicken Breast, diced
  • 1 Onion (160 g), diced
  • 3 Carrots (300 g), peeled & diced
  • 2 Potatoes (250 g), peeled & diced
  • 1/4 Pumpkin (250 g), peeled & diced
  • 1 MasterFoods™ Mild Chicken Curry Recipe Base
  • 1/2 cup Light Thickened Cream (125 mL)
  • 1 cup dry Brown Rice

How To Cook:
1. Heat oil in pan and cook chicken until brown.
2. Place cooked chicken, vegetables and Recipe Base into a slow cooker and stir.
3. Cook for 4 hours on high or 8 hours on low.
4. Add cream and stir through 10 mins before serving.
5. Meanwhile, cook rice and serve with your MasterFoods™ Mild Chicken Curry.

Please note slow cookers vary. Recipe is based on using a 3 litre slow cooker.

For Something Different:
Turn it up a notch! Add 1 tsp of our ground Turmeric.


Blended with MasterFoods™ Herbs & Spices


Make Dinnertime Matter with MasterFoods™.

Products.RichDescription:
Create simple, wholesome dinners the whole family will love.
Create a delicious, fragrant base to your dinner creations with MasterFoods™ Savoury mince Recipe Base. Made with carefully selected tomatoes, herbs and spices to deliver the perfect balance of flavours. Just add lean beef mince, onion, peas, corn and carrot for a delicious meal you can enjoy as part of your daily diet.

Preparation: 5 mins | Cook: 10 mins | Serves: 4

What You'll Need:
  • Canola Oil Spray
  • 1 Onion (160 g), sliced
  • 500 g lean Beef Mince
  • 2 cups Frozen Mixed Vegetables (340 g)
  • 1 MasterFoods™ Savoury Mince Recipe Base
  • 1/4 cup Water (60 mL) 1 cup dry Brown Rice
How To Cook:
1. Heat pan on medium heat. Spray with oil and cook onion until soft.
2. Add mince and cook until browned.
3. Stir in frozen vegetables, Recipe Base and water, simmer uncovered for 5 minutes or until vegetables are soft.
4. Meanwhile, cook rice to serve with your MasterFoods™ Savoury Mince.

Products.FullDescription: Masterfoods Thai Green Curry Recipe Base
Products.RichDescription:
Create an easy, delicious Thai Green Curry with a hint of lime.


Create a quick, delicious family meal with MasterFoods™ Thai Green Curry Recipe Base. A carefully created blend of lemongrass, lime, chilli and coriander. Create a mid-week meal in under 30 minutes that's full of flavour and fresh ingredients. Just add lean chicken breast, green beans, zucchinis and light coconut milk for a delicious meal you can enjoy as part of your daily diet.

Preparation: 10 mins | Cook: 10 mins | Serves: 4.

What You'll Need:

  • Canola Oil Spray
  • 500 g Lean Chicken Breast, sliced
  • 1 MasterFoods™ Thai Green Curry Recipe Base
  • 1 Red Capsicum (200 g), peeled & sliced
  • 3 Carrots (300 g), peeled & sliced
  • 1 head Broccoli (200 g), cut into florets
  • 2/3 cup Light Coconut Milk (165 mL)
  • 1 cup dry Brown Rice

How To Cook:
1. Spray a pan with oil, add chicken and cook until browned.
2. Add Recipe Base, heat and then add vegetables.
3. Add light coconut milk, bring to the boil and gently simmer for 5 minutes.
4. Meanwhile, cook rice.
5. Serve MasterFoods™ Thai Green Curry over steaming rice.

For Something Different:
For extra veggies, add 400 g green beans, trimmed and halved, in step 2.


Blended with MasterFoods™ Herbs & Spices


Make Dinnertime Matter with MasterFoods™.
